    Return PythonShutdownFailure with error as "Platform implementation required"

Process python_acquire_gil that takes runtime as PythonRuntime returns Dictionary[String, Any]:
    Note: Acquire Python Global Interpreter Lock
    Note: PyGILState_Ensure() or PyEval_RestoreThread()
    Return dict_utils.create_dict_with_entries with entries as [("success", false), ("error", "Platform implementation required")]

Process python_release_gil that takes runtime as PythonRuntime returns Dictionary[String, Any]:
    Note: Release Python Global Interpreter Lock  
    Note: PyGILState_Release() or PyEval_SaveThread()
    Return dict_utils.create_dict_with_entries with entries as [("success", false), ("error", "Platform implementation required")]

Process python_get_version that takes interpreter as Integer returns Dictionary[String, Any]:
    Note: Get Python version string
    Note: Py_GetVersion()
